@startuml
title Raw Material Order

actor ProductionManager
participant ManagementSystem
participant Warehouse
participant Supplier

ProductionManager -> ManagementSystem : Check inventory

ManagementSystem -> Warehouse : Get material stock
Warehouse --> ManagementSystem : Stock quantity

ManagementSystem --> ProductionManager : Material shortage

ProductionManager -> ManagementSystem : Create purchase order

ManagementSystem -> Supplier : Send purchase order
Supplier --> ManagementSystem : Confirm order

ManagementSystem --> ProductionManager : Order registered

@enduml
